way people act.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's mind boggling.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"J.B., you are still the man.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Time gets us all.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also Jason Nolf is a dog!\\\"\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Nolf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jason Nolf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Nolf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Nolf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burroughs, 35, likely goes down as one of the greatest American wrestlers in history, with a long list of accolades on his r\\u00e9sum\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Burroughs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1112628541307662e-20, \"text\": \"Burroughs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Burroughs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Burroughs\"}, {\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Wrestlers\", \"score\": 0.9999945473640264, \"rank\": 5.450211953576997e-06, \"text\": \"American wrestlers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Wrestlers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Wrestlers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, he's now failed to make the past two Olympic teams, with a loss to Kyle Dake in 2020 and then falling to Nolf ahead of the 2024 games.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Dake\", \"score\"