n show me 'F***' from like 200 meters, I am not going to punch you.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when you are close to me, it's, like automatically.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am from Russia.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2269, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9326416391081825, \"rank\": 0.06627935839860394, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not do that, please, or I am going to go to prison in U.S.\\\"  It sounds like Cormier agrees with Tsarukyan's actions, especially after what he witnessed during the U.S. Olympic team trials in wrestling on Friday.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Cormier\", \"score\": 0.999999983701855, \"rank\": 1.6046285892422953e-08, \"text\": \"Cormier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Cormier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Cormier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A daily roundup of UFC and MMA news and results  This is the title for the native ad  Umar Nurmagomedov takes on Deiveson Figueiredo at UFC 324 in January  Paddy Pimblett and Arman Tsarukyan take shots at each other.\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.435236720460022e-30, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2523, \"title\": \"http: